^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Let's discuss the bidding. Ann has 19 Starting Points (16 HCP, 2 length 1 quality suit = 19). 3@D bid is just at the top of the range (17-19) but a bit misleading. Sandy might pass with 5 spades and a singleton diamond and you could easily miss 4S (which you did).|
